<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:40%; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in; height:35px; background-color:#d9d9d9; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Downward pressure applied to top of head with extended neck and rotates to affected side </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:23%; padding:0in 0in 0in 0in; height:35px; background-color:#d9d9d9; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Reproducible pain beyond shoulder</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><br/>
			 </p>
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="vertical-align:baseline"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Neck pain alone is not specific</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
